(23-Nov-95)

 - {s}  ADDED   'FrameIHack'

 - {s}  ADDED   'BorderBlank' for Kickstart 2.x.

(21-Nov-95)

 - {s}  FIXED   bug in 'CycleScreens Back2Front' hotkey if only one screen
