(21-Apr-97)

 - {m}  FIXED   checking of ARQ-Mode for the Reqtools-Patch.
                >> Rene Bour <<

(17-Apr-97)

 - {m}  FIXED   wrong On/Off tag values in the ScreenManager.

(03-Apr-97)

 - {s}  FIXED   some bugs. Enable of ScreenManager was not correct.

(27-Mar-97)

 - {m}  FIXED   little bug that not all Dri-Pens are showed

(22-Mar-97)

 - {m}  FIXED   hopefully all bugs with disable/enable functions

(15-Mar-97)

 - {m}  FIXED   reading of the prefsfile. In V1.30b2 the activation of the
                function was trashed.

(10-Feb-97)

 - {m}  ADDED   SaveAs function

(01-Feb-97)

 - {m}  FIXED   crash if no IF condition given
                >> Ian Kumlien <<

(20-Jan-97)

 - {m}  ADDED   new ScreenManager Preferences (hard work:)

